{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Nintendo Mengumumkan Peripheral Terbaru Untuk Switch: Nintendo Labo!","content":"<p>Nama Nintendo tentunya sudah tidak asing lagi bagi para <em>gamer</em> di seluruh dunia. Nah kali ini Nintendo membawa sebuah produk baru yang bernama Nintendo Labo! Nintendo Labo sendiri adalah berbagai jenis aksesoris yang terbuat dari kertas karton kardus, yang dapat dirakit sendiri oleh <em>gamer</em> dan digabungkan dengan konsol Nintendo Switch. Dengan tambahan <em>peripheral</em> baru ini, akan membuat game Nintendo Switch menjadi lebih interaktif.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41292\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41292\" data-attachment-id=\"41292\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/attachment/nintendo-labo-01-bike/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-01-bike.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendo labo 01 bike\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-01-bike-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-01-bike.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41292\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-01-bike.jpg\" alt=\"nintendo labo 01 bike\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-01-bike.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-01-bike-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41292\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div>\n<p>Nintendo memberi nama aksesoris ini Toy-Con. Toy-Con sendiri dijual dalam dua macam paket, yaitu Variety Kit dan Robot Kit. Untuk Variety Kit, <em>gamer</em> akan mendapatkan lima macam Toy-Con, yaitu piano dengan 13 tuts, tongkat pancing, stang motor, mobil RC, dan rumah-rumahan beserta <em>cartridge</em> game yang dapat dimainkan dengan masing-masing Toy-Con tersebut.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41293\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41293\" data-attachment-id=\"41293\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/attachment/nintendo-labo-02-piano/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-02-piano.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendo labo 02 piano\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-02-piano-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-02-piano.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41293\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-02-piano.jpg\" alt=\"nintendo labo 02 piano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-02-piano.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-02-piano-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41293\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div>\n<p>Masing-masing Toy-Con tersebut juga menggunakan berbagai macam teknologi yang terdapat pada Nintendo Switch dan Joy-Con-nya untuk melakukan berbagai hal. Misalnya dalam Toy-Con piano, Nintendo memanfaatkan <em>IR blaster</em> yang terdapat pada Joy-Con untuk mengenali gerakan tuts piano dan mengirimkan sinyal pada Switch yang akan memainkan nada serta memberikan <em>feedback</em> visual yang sesuai.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41294\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41294\" data-attachment-id=\"41294\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/attachment/nintendo-labo-03-rod/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-03-rod.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendo labo 03 rod\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-03-rod-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-03-rod.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41294\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-03-rod.jpg\" alt=\"nintendo labo 03 rod\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-03-rod.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-03-rod-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41294\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div>\n<p>Semua Toy-Con yang ada saat ini tidak menggunakan komponen elektronik sama sekali dalam penggunaannya, selain Joy-Con dan konsol Nintendo Switch sendiri tentunya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41296\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41296\" data-attachment-id=\"41296\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/attachment/nintendo-labo-04-robot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-04-robot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendo labo 04 robot\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-04-robot-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-04-robot.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41296\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-04-robot.jpg\" alt=\"nintendo labo 04 robot\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-04-robot.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-04-robot-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41296\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div>\n<p>Nah, untuk Robot Kit sendiri pemain akan bermain sebagai sebuah robot yang dapat bergerak sesuai dengan gerakan bro sis di dunia nyata. Robot Kit ini berbentuk sebuah tas yang dikenakan oleh <em>gamer</em>, berbagai macam alat yang dipasang di kaki dan tangan, serta aksesoris kepala. Sekali lagi, Toy-Con Robot Kit ini tidak menggunakan komponen elektronik sama sekali, selain Joy-Con dan Nintendo Switch. Paket Robot Kit juga bakal dilengkapi <em>cartridge</em> game khusus.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41303\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41303\" data-attachment-id=\"41303\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/attachment/nintendo-labo-05-rc/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-05-rc.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendo labo 05 rc\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-05-rc-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-05-rc.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41303\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-05-rc.jpg\" alt=\"nintendo labo 05 rc\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-05-rc.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-05-rc-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41303\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div>\n<p>Selain aksesoris yang bisa dibeli saat Labo diluncurkan tanggal 20 April 2018 nanti, kalau memperhatikan <em>trailer</em> Nintendo Labo sepertinya bakal ada lebih banyak lagi jenis Toy-Con yang akan dibuat oleh Nintendo kedepannya. Misalnya ada Toy-Con berbentuk burung, setir mobil beserta pedal gas-nya, kamera, senjata, alat musik drum, tuas kendali pesawat, dan masih banyak lagi yang dipamerkan oleh Nintendo dalam <em>trailer</em> tersebut. <em>Gamer</em> juga dapat berkreasi untuk membuat Toy-Con mereka menjadi lebih menarik dan unik dengan mewarnai serta menempelkan berbagai macam karton hiasan yang telah disediakan dalam paket Variety Kit, atau dengan membeli Customization Set.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41304\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41304\" data-attachment-id=\"41304\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-mengumumkan-peripheral-terbaru-untuk-switch-nintendo-labo/attachment/nintendo-labo-06-house/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-06-house.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendo labo 06 house\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-06-house-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-06-house.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41304\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-06-house.jpg\" alt=\"nintendo labo 06 house\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-06-house.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/nintendo-labo-06-house-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41304\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div>\n<p>Nintendo lagi-lagi membuat sebuah inovasi yang sangat menonjolkan kekuatan serta kreatifitas yang luar biasa pada produk mereka. Nintendo Labo bisa bro sis tebus seharga US$69.99 untuk Variety Kit, sementara Robot Kit dihargai US$ 79.99. Kalau bro sis punya semangat <em>do-it-yourself</em> yang kuat, Nintendo juga bakal memberikan pola Toy-Con-nya secara gratis untuk di-<em>print</em> sendiri di atas kertas kardus!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/P3Bd3HUMkyU\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Penasaran dengan cara main Nintendo Labo? Simak langsung <em>trailer</em>-nya berikut ini. Bro sis sendiri tertarik dengan Toy-Con jenis apa?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cc4056c3-8971-542c-8830-b365d5d5cab1"}}}